---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Contact - Atiquzzaman Soikat">
  <!-- Profile Image -->
  <div class="w-full mx-auto md:w-2/5 mb-8">
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-600 rounded-full opacity-10 blur-xl transform scale-110"></div>
      <img
        src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1593663?v=4"
        alt="Atiquzzaman Soikat"
        class="relative w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover border-4 border-white shadow-xl"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Profile Info -->
  <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Hi, I'm <span class="text-brandingColor">Md Atiquzzaman Soikat</span></h1>
  <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 font-semibold mb-6">Senior Software Engineer & CTO at ReformedTech</p>
  <div
  class="m-auto text-center mt-4 mb-4 justify-center flex flex-col items-center w-full space-x-5 space-y-8 lg:space-y-0 lg:flex-row"
>
  <a
    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/atiquzzaman-soikat/"
    aria-label="Connect on LinkedIn"
    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-2 py-2 font-black text-center text-white shadow-xl xl:px-12 xl:text-2xl lg:w-auto hover:bg-green-600 bg-blue-600"
  >
    Connect on LinkedIn
    <svg
      class="w-6 h-6 ml-2"
      aria-hidden="true"
      fill="currentColor"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    >
      <path
        d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"
      ></path>
    </svg>
  </a>
  <a
    href="Resume-of- Md-Atiquzzaman-Soikat.pdf"
    aria-label="View Resume"
    class="inline-flex lg:pl-10 items-center text-lg text-gray-600 underline transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-brandingColor"
    >View Resume</a
  >
</div>
  <!-- Introduction -->
  <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
    <p>
      With over a decade of web development expertise, I've most recently served as Lead Frontend Developer at Skipper Hospitality, while also co-founding ReformedTech where I currently serve as CTO.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <span class="tech-highlight">JavaScript</span> has been my primary programming language throughout my career, complemented by experience in <span class="tech-highlight">PHP</span>, <span class="tech-highlight">Python</span>, <span class="tech-highlight">Ruby</span>, and <span class="tech-highlight">Java</span>. While I've extensively worked with <span class="tech-highlight">React</span> and <span class="tech-highlight">Vue.js</span>, <span class="tech-highlight">Svelte</span> has emerged as my preferred frontend framework over the past four years, thanks to its elegant approach to UI development and exceptional developer experience.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Now a days, my technical focus centers on <span class="tech-highlight">Frontend Infrastructure</span> and tooling that enhances developer experience. I'm also expanding my expertise in <span class="tech-highlight">DevOps</span> practices, bridging the gap between development and operations to streamline deployment workflows. I'm passionate about <span class="tech-highlight">Jamstack</span> architecture and take pride in creating performant, user-friendly, and scalable web applications that deliver exceptional experiences from development through to production.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Beyond coding, I maintain a balanced life through gaming, cooking, and quality time with friends and family.
    </p>
  </div>
<!-- MVP Quick-Start CTA Section -->
<section class="my-12 mx-auto max-w-4xl hidden">
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 via-purple-600 to-blue-600  overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
    <div class="p-8 text-white">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Have an idea?</h2>
          <div class="text-2xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold mb-2">
            Create an MVP in just <span class="relative">
              three weeks
              <svg class="absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-full" height="4" viewBox="0 0 100 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M1 5.5C20.6667 2.16667 68.3333 -0.499999 99 8.50001" stroke="white" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xl opacity-90">
            Starting from <span class="font-bold tech-highlight">$3000</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/services" class="mt-6 md:mt-0 inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white text-black font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-colors shadow-md">
          Learn More
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
    .tech-highlight {
    position: relative;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .tech-highlight::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -2px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4f46e5 0%, #818cf8 100%);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transform: perspective(10px) rotateX(5deg);
    opacity: 0.6;
    z-index: -1;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .tech-highlight:hover::after {
    height: 8px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    transform: perspective(10px) rotateX(8deg) translateY(-1px);
  }
</style>